SEARCH
Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures

Class StructureSnapshot

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures.StructureSnapshot
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStructureConst, IPropertyHolderConst
@ThreadSafe public final class StructureSnapshot extends Object implements IStructureConst
Represents a (read-only) snapshot of a structure at a particular point in time.

All access to this class is thread safe and does not lock.

Please read the documentation of nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures for more information about the structure system.
